content: Hey everyone, I'm Morgan. I have some experience with Python and C, but I gave Rust a chance and have spent the last few months falling in love with it. I'm a math/physics undergraduate student, and my main interest when it comes to CS/programming is math-related programming, especially symbolic computation.
have you heard of SIGSAM? they put out the TOMS journal, it's a lot of reading but relatively interesting overall, the undergrad membership rates are good as well
